{"tid":2268412,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"日日鼻塞 醫生問考唔考慮做手術","createTime":"2020-11-02T20:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T18:05:05.000Z","uid":213295,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"192472784a87708da582087228bc45d697b4c957","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:39:10.000Z","msg":"我係經常鼻塞、頭痛，鼻分泌物多。<br />\n睇左幾年耳鼻喉科，佢話可以考慮下做唔做手術<br />\n有冇巴打做過呢類型手術，可以分享下依家個鼻情況點嗎？"},{"pid":"c4185d5da1ff52b5fa0bee23309395f3ccd2e63c","tid":2268412,"uid":83874,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"192472784a87708da582087228bc45d697b4c957","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:39:10.000Z","msg":"我係經常鼻塞、頭痛，鼻分泌物多。<br />\n睇左幾年耳鼻喉科，佢話可以考慮下做唔做手術<br />\n有冇巴打做過呢類型手術，可以分享下依家個鼻情況點嗎？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"有冇試試中醫調理?"},{"pid":"237d9a5a5235c5469cc85a7ddf58cdda4f6879c9","tid":2268412,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:46:06.000Z","msg":"有冇照鼻竇？"},{"pid":"c9523388b5dde156b124b44523144ffdc8f5f937","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4185d5da1ff52b5fa0bee23309395f3ccd2e63c","tid":2268412,"uid":83874,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"192472784a87708da582087228bc45d697b4c957","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:39:10.000Z","msg":"我係經常鼻塞、頭痛，鼻分泌物多。<br />\n睇左幾年耳鼻喉科，佢話可以考慮下做唔做手術<br />\n有冇巴打做過呢類型手術，可以分享下依家個鼻情況點嗎？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"有冇試試中醫調理?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:51:51.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a759850eb25cb3b33643692116c604e3e1016a06","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237d9a5a5235c5469cc85a7ddf58cdda4f6879c9","tid":2268412,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:46:06.000Z","msg":"有冇照鼻竇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:52:28.000Z","msg":"佢話鼻入面偏腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ec48eaf342acbbd6f77b0bb0bb357166039dfa","tid":2268412,"uid":83874,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c9523388b5dde156b124b44523144ffdc8f5f937","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4185d5da1ff52b5fa0bee23309395f3ccd2e63c","tid":2268412,"uid":83874,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"192472784a87708da582087228bc45d697b4c957","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:39:10.000Z","msg":"我係經常鼻塞、頭痛，鼻分泌物多。<br />\n睇左幾年耳鼻喉科，佢話可以考慮下做唔做手術<br />\n有冇巴打做過呢類型手術，可以分享下依家個鼻情況點嗎？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"有冇試試中醫調理?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:51:51.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:58:06.000Z","msg":"如果唔想手術, 可以試試中醫調理睇下有冇效果"},{"pid":"74f01bae15dcc6decc37017ad7c723efdcf50c91","tid":2268412,"uid":306548,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:39:06.000Z","msg":"我5年前都有呢個問題<br />\n睇醫生話鼻竇腫 個鼻都越來越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我每日都會按摩個鼻 想捏細啲<br />\n一開始冇用, 仲大左, 但2年前開始好左<br />\n我都唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家個鼻細左好多, 都keep住捏<br />\n我覺得關香港太潮濕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba87e037412bcdd4cb3bc2fed944b04932de867","tid":2268412,"uid":326848,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T23:01:17.000Z","msg":"純分享<br />\n我鼻中隔唔正 仲入面成日都腫 <br />\n一有煙味 裝香 都會打黑次「噴涕」<br />\n但係發現 離開香港個鼻就會無事<br />\n所有鼻敏感 不藥而癒💪<br />\n可以試下食維他命C ,B雜"},{"pid":"bebf779898ab5356371567f2ed588c382104e20f","tid":2268412,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a759850eb25cb3b33643692116c604e3e1016a06","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237d9a5a5235c5469cc85a7ddf58cdda4f6879c9","tid":2268412,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:46:06.000Z","msg":"有冇照鼻竇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T20:52:28.000Z","msg":"佢話鼻入面偏腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"用咗藥(Nasonex)先啦。加洗鼻，唔得先做。"},{"pid":"458554298b91a00c62d65622c0b4a3e98f493acb","tid":2268412,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"我以前都係<br />\n而家搬左去乾燥國家住<br />\n如果唔計病左果陣 基本上無塞過咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0ff94e8a9f7e868bb2cdba26f6ad364d912d58","tid":2268412,"uid":6562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ba87e037412bcdd4cb3bc2fed944b04932de867","tid":2268412,"uid":326848,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T23:01:17.000Z","msg":"純分享<br />\n我鼻中隔唔正 仲入面成日都腫 <br />\n一有煙味 裝香 都會打黑次「噴涕」<br />\n但係發現 離開香港個鼻就會無事<br />\n所有鼻敏感 不藥而癒💪<br />\n可以試下食維他命C ,B雜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"咦我同你一樣 鼻中隔彎曲<br />\n本身係外國讀書無事 翻香港就一直唔舒服<br />\n想問你係KEEP住日日食? 有無話邊隻牌子推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日訓覺都訓唔好呀唉 黎緊仲諗住睇耳鼻喉醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3b5d3b5c9c7a0b060e51ea14b93b87cd3edfe6","tid":2268412,"uid":103962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"我都係鼻中隔彎曲，下個星期就做手術"},{"pid":"0f0194f9f50327a01f5f4005b8d3c7fed742370b","tid":2268412,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"細個成日流鼻血<br />\n有次睇醫生話因為鼻敏感加鼻唔知乜春容易爆d血管，可以做個手術<br />\n做緊果時feel到個鼻入面有d痛，又好似有d熱，個feel好似喺鼻入面爆火花咁，唔知佢燒定電定剪走d乜<br />\n做完手術真係一年流都無一次鼻血<br />\n但鼻敏感勁咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ac6deaaa7462478b23af24a333aaf413a5d332","tid":2268412,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"兩邊都塞定單邊"},{"pid":"c651b8813c908b4c4d5be4ab9957380adbe5ac1b","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32ac6deaaa7462478b23af24a333aaf413a5d332","tid":2268412,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"兩邊都塞定單邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:16:05.000Z","msg":"都塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a8b57af67aef3772ce00bda70b9ebf7cf48c0e","tid":2268412,"uid":326848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d0ff94e8a9f7e868bb2cdba26f6ad364d912d58","tid":2268412,"uid":6562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ba87e037412bcdd4cb3bc2fed944b04932de867","tid":2268412,"uid":326848,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T23:01:17.000Z","msg":"純分享<br />\n我鼻中隔唔正 仲入面成日都腫 <br />\n一有煙味 裝香 都會打黑次「噴涕」<br />\n但係發現 離開香港個鼻就會無事<br />\n所有鼻敏感 不藥而癒💪<br />\n可以試下食維他命C ,B雜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"咦我同你一樣 鼻中隔彎曲<br />\n本身係外國讀書無事 翻香港就一直唔舒服<br />\n想問你係KEEP住日日食? 有無話邊隻牌子推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日訓覺都訓唔好呀唉 黎緊仲諗住睇耳鼻喉醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"其實 都係啲普通 維他命"},{"pid":"c59de082a70e47f34a858a620eab9bb40eecb306","tid":2268412,"uid":326848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3b5d3b5c9c7a0b060e51ea14b93b87cd3edfe6","tid":2268412,"uid":103962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"我都係鼻中隔彎曲，下個星期就做手術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T00:04:39.000Z","msg":"我幾年前約左，做之前驚到發燒， 見醫生 醫生話唔影響生活 可以唔搞。"},{"pid":"9d2a53b287d61c75591d52b82bf2313afe70ae7d","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"日日訓都要靠通鼻靈啲friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c09ea6c88fe5574a342ea531de4020e90f396d2","tid":2268412,"uid":36686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2a53b287d61c75591d52b82bf2313afe70ae7d","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"日日訓都要靠通鼻靈啲friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:25:15.000Z","msg":"試下安鼻適"},{"pid":"b05414c8fe815c29ea96298962faab121307ca69","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c09ea6c88fe5574a342ea531de4020e90f396d2","tid":2268412,"uid":36686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2a53b287d61c75591d52b82bf2313afe70ae7d","tid":2268412,"uid":213295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"日日訓都要靠通鼻靈啲friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:25:15.000Z","msg":"試下安鼻適"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:26:32.000Z","msg":"Nazal?我噴左2,3年<br />\n基本日日噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206089603b129317c2a9fb32ca4911b26134042e","tid":2268412,"uid":9231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:42:52.000Z","msg":"睇左幾個醫生<br />\n個個都講唔同<br />\n有d又話要做手術，有d又話路駛<br />\n都唔知要點搞<br />\n由頭塞到大，一訓教就變到口呼吸"},{"pid":"eed002e0b68dd265dc9713236348508e24519ae7","tid":2268412,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:57:11.000Z","msg":"做，我上年先做完嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過你要預3日(72小時)無得用鼻呼吸<br />\n<br />\n想知做完手術嘅後話我先再講，畢生難忘，包你睇文字都覺得刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n失去個鼻先知道就連飲水都困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c77d4a6c392caf2be54dbaee2d1345111b9870","tid":2268412,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:58:13.000Z","msg":"做<br />\n做咗有5年無鼻塞<br />\n5年後復發再做"},{"pid":"5765cd9249ba2a8cced78f84609abe50809d66bf","tid":2268412,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T21:29:20.000Z","msg":"我都係鼻入面勁腫<br />\n後來發現一離開香港就冇事<br />\n講緊去深圳都已經有改善<br />\n去台韓日更加係舒暢哂<br />\n<br />\n而家有keep住做尖<br />\n情況好咗<br />\n但一唔做運動又會塞返<br />\n<br />\n另外有食開煙<br />\n食唔同牌子都會影響個鼻<br />\n<br />\n所以真係唔一定要開刀<br />\n而開刀都可以復發<br />\n至於中醫嗰啲唔使試<br />\n冇撚用的"},{"pid":"923fe8d848e69d255c06a26d7957dad230eecd4b","tid":2268412,"uid":381374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed002e0b68dd265dc9713236348508e24519ae7","tid":2268412,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T20:57:11.000Z","msg":"做，我上年先做完嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過你要預3日(72小時)無得用鼻呼吸<br />\n<br />\n想知做完手術嘅後話我先再講，畢生難忘，包你睇文字都覺得刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n失去個鼻先知道就連飲水都困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T21:49:47.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}